title: SCP-5336 fan comic
content:
[[>]]
[[module Rate]]
[[/>]]


The following story was written by [[*user anactualcrow]] and illustrated by myself for gift exchange. This story can be found here: [[[https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5336 |SCP-5336]]]. I highly suggest you give this person's work a read. They are a fantastic author, an amazing story teller, with a wonderful blend of comedy and surrealism. I simply can’t overstate how much this person's work deserves some love! Please give the rest of their work a read! [[[https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/anactualcrow |Crows author page]]].
